ern gender roles that animated the century to come.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aMotion picture actors and actresseszCaliforniazLos Angeles. 0aMotion pictures and womenzUnited States. 0aWomen in the motion picture industryzCaliforniazLos AngelesxHistoryy20th century. 7aHISTORY / United States / General.2bisacsh  a20th century film history.  a20th century women.  aacademic books.  aamerican history.  abirth of los angeles.  abook club reads.  abooks for film lovers.  abooks for history lovers.  adiscrimination of women.  adiscussion books.  aearly modern american history.  aeasy to read.  aeducational books.  afeminism.  afilm capital of the united states.  agender studies.  ahistory of hollywood.  ahollywood sex scandal.  alearning while reading.  amen and women.  amodern gender roles.  apage turner.  apost war cinema industry.  asex.  athe great war.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z97831106904220 cprintz978052027408240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052095368040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520953680423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520953680/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY